I"ø<h2 id="category-page">Category Page</h2>

<p>To create a category page listing your robots you will need to create a robot category page.</p>

<p>Create a page, for example <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">robots.md</code>, with the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">layout: robot-category</code> in the front matter. You can set the sort order of the robots using <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sort: title</code> to sort by the title, or by any setting in your robot pages, such as price, rating or any custom front matter tags you wish to set.</p>

<div class="language-yaml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="na">title</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">Robots</span>
<span class="na">subtitle</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">Check out our range of robots</span>
<span class="na">layout</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">robot-category</span>
<span class="na">show_sidebar</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="no">false</span>
<span class="na">sort</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">title</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><a href="/bulma-clean-theme/robots/">View example Category page</a></p>
